description: The CompTIA A+ 801 Course, powered by Calibrate, helps beginning and prospective IT professionals learn the fundamentals of computer technology installation and configuration of PCs, laptops and related hardware. Individuals who successfully complete this self-paced online course will have the foundational knowledge needed to pass the 801 section of the CompTIA A+ certification exam and will be prepared to begin study for the CompTIA A+ 802 exam.
title: CompTIA A+: 220-801
